The '''19 Eylül Stadium''' is a multi-use stadium in [[Ordu]], [[Turkey]]. It is currently used mostly for [[association football|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Orduspor]]. The stadium holds 11,024 people and was built in 1967.<ref name="ws">[http://www.tff.org.tr/Default.aspx?pageID=394&stadID=153 TFF: Ordu 19 Eylül Stadı] {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/62EglECzL?url=http://www.tff.org.tr/Default.aspx?pageID=394&stadID=153 |date=October 6, 2011 }}</ref>
