The '''Dub Farris Athletic Complex''' is a sporting complex with the '''Dub Farris Stadium''' owned by the [[Northside ISD]] located in [[San Antonio, Texas]].
The complex is known for its 10,568-seat [[American football|football]] & [[soccer]] stadium but it is also home to a large [[natatorium]]. In 2010, NISD announced a three-year agreement that allowed the [[UTSA Roadrunners football]] team to use the stadium for practice.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goutsa.com/ViewArticle.dbml?SPSID=315549&SPID=34919&DB_OEM_ID=13100&ATCLID=204967789 |title=Banner Day for UTSA Football |publisher=[[UTSA Roadrunners]] |date=2010-07-13 |accessdate=2010-08-10}}</ref>
