'''Jeunesse Sportive Madinet Skikda''' ({{lang-ar|الشبيبة الرياضية لمدينة سكيكدة}}), known as '''JSM Skikda''' or simply '''JSMS'''  for short, is a [[Association football|football]] club based in the city of [[Skikda]]. The club was founded in 1936 and its colours are black and white. Their home stadium, the [[Stade 20 Août 1955 (Skikda)|Stade 20 Août 1955]], has a capacity of some 30,000 spectators. The club is currently playing in the [[Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 2]].

==Honours==
*'''[[Algerian Cup]]'''
::'''Runners-up (1)''': [[1966–67 Algerian Cup|1967]]
*'''League of Constantine'''
::'''Winners (1)''': 1953


